
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 05 of Thoracic MRT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Lung parenchyma pathology' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' butoon is enabled
And a multiple selection localizer is enabled
And 'Consolidation/Atelectasis' radio button is enabled
And 'Mass' radio button is enabled

When I click on the localizer
And I select all the 6 parts
Then all the 6 parts are selected and turn red


When I select 'Mass' radio button
Then 'Size' input field is enabled

When I enter any value from 1 to 300 in 'Size' input field
Then '2nd plane' input field is enabled

When I enter any value from 1 to 300 in 'Size' input field
Then '3rd plane' input field is enabled
